      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is currently not in reliable running order. The engine has difficulty starting and staying idle, and there are visible fluid leaks that will require immediate mechanical attention. The exterior shows significant wear, including noticeable rust spots on the wheel arches and several dents along the passenger side. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with some tearing, and several electronic features are non-functional. This would be an ideal project for a mechanic or someone looking for a parts car.",
