      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a reliable companion. It\u2019s in really solid shape and drives like a dream\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable car without the brand-new price tag. It\u2019s got a few tiny signs of being loved, but it\u2019s super clean and ready to hit the road for its next adventure. You\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
