    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving powerplant delivers 414 hp with an 8,400 RPM redline, mated to a precise 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and the M Variable Differential Lock for superior lateral grip and corner-exit traction. Recent preventative maintenance includes a rod bearing service and throttle actuator replacement, ensuring the mechanical integrity of the valvetrain and induction system. The vehicle retains its factory carbon fiber roof for a lower center of gravity and features a well-sorted suspension with consistent damping profiles. This is a mechanically sound example of BMW M's peak hydraulic-steering era.",
      "price": 34500.0,
